412
00:20:07,524 --> 00:20:08,272
Okay.

413
00:20:11,901 --> 00:20:12,544
She's fine.

414
00:20:12,852 --> 00:20:14,795
She has the potential to be a spy.

415
00:20:14,945 --> 00:20:16,639
