449
00:21:15,475 --> 00:21:16,577
To live normally.

450
00:21:16,799 --> 00:21:17,745
To live normally...?

451
00:21:17,802 --> 00:21:18,189
That's right.

452
00:21:18,231 --> 00:21:18,847
