562
00:25:59,453 --> 00:26:00,404
What...

563
00:26:01,175 --> 00:26:02,024
Hey?

564
00:26:02,538 --> 00:26:03,450
Why were you crying again?

565
00:26:03,489 --> 00:26:04,954
